item.title: 📝 Blogging: A Brand New Start 🛣️
item.description: State of the Affairs: 2020 - 2023 I had only two articles on this blog for the past 2-3 years, with very limited activity, if almost none at all. Part of this was due to personal reasons, I was busy to say the very least: Spending time taking care of long-lasting health concerns. I have undergone a dozen of procedures, some were elective, some others were really not. I had to do what was needed for myself.
